<Layout>
  <main class="mt-12 md:mt-36 mx-5 md:mx-10">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-3 font-firaCodeBold">Hey, I'm Hamza</h1>
    <h2 class="text-sky-500 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-openSansBold">
      Front-End Developer
    </h2>
    <p class="my-4 md:w-[45rem] leading-8 font-bold font-poppins text-xl">
      I'm passionate about the dynamic world of web development, with a
